# 止蝕
(pos: 動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或買賣入面，當價格下跌時，將資產賣出以減少損失嘅行為（量詞：次）
eng:to cut losses; to stop loss
<eg>
yue:股價跌咗咁多，佢決定止蝕離場。 (gaa1 gyun1 dit3 zo2 gam3 do1, keoi5 gwok3 ding6 zi6 si1 sik1 lei4 coeng4.)
eng:Since the stock price has dropped so much, he decided to cut his losses and leave the market.

yue:唔好貪心，見到跌就要懂得止蝕。 (m4 hou2 taam1 sam1, gin3 dou3 dit3 jiu3 jiu3 dung2 dak1 zi6 sik1.)
eng:Don't be greedy; when you see a drop, you should know how to cut your losses. [end of text]


